/*
During the operation, our platform communicates to restaurants about the performance of their dishes. 
So we need someone who is able to count the dishes that have never been sold on the platform.
在營運上，平台會定期和餐廳溝通不同餐點的表現。
因此我們會需要小幫手幫忙統計，找出在各餐廳中我們平台上從未賣出的餐點。
*/

# way1
SELECT m.merchant, m.item 
  FROM merchants AS m 
  LEFT JOIN deliveries AS d ON m.item_id = d.item_id 
 WHERE d.order_id IS NULL;
 
# way2
SELECT item
FROM deliveries
WHERE item IS NULL;
